1403
01:33:27,047 --> 01:33:30,039
That triggered things off,
we got it...

1404
01:33:31,287 --> 01:33:35,121
Why send
an undernourished kid home?

1405
01:33:35,287 --> 01:33:37,039
What's the country doing?

1406
01:33:37,807 --> 01:33:40,196
