about 18% underfed kids.

1409
01:33:48,647 --> 01:33:52,322
Now it's close to 80%.

1410
01:34:30,927 --> 01:34:34,363
In garbage dumps,
all those abandoned children,

1411
01:34:34,527 --> 01:34:37,200
pregnant girls of 14 or 15,

1412
01:34:37,367 --> 01:34:40,006
the kids called "nobody's kids",

1413
01:34:40,607 --> 01:34:42,563
only eat every other day.

1414
01:34:42,727 --> 01:34:45,560
Should I tell a 14-year old mother:

1415
01:34:45,727 --> 01:34:48,321
"To fight your baby's diarrhea,

1416
