1446
01:36:32,327 --> 01:36:36,286
90% are paupers,
and 10% own everything.

1447
01:36:36,687 --> 01:36:39,155
That's not a system...

1448
01:36:39,327 --> 01:36:42,478
I'm 54 and it's always the same.

1449
01:36:42,647 --> 01:36:44,444
That same old austerity.

1450
01:36:44,607 --> 01:36:47,644
They always go back
to the same things.

1451
01:36:47,887 --> 01:36:49,878
